                <p>Select the type of service you need from our range of options.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <h3>Step 2: Book a Time</h3>
                <p>Pick a time slot that fits your schedule, and we'll confirm your booking.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
